divs: Sighting DetailsSat Sep 8, 2012 I was out side walking my dogs around 6:30 p.m and when I looked to the east I noted a round white object no sound moving slow. It made no change in direction that I could see and pasted over a tree line out of sight. I'm not good with distance it didn't seem to be very high in the sky. Not as high as a plane so I'm not sure what it was. I just wanted to put this out there incase anyone else seem something.
